data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of Cypress, TX! This stunning single-story residence offers the perfect blend of modern and comfort. Flowing airy, open layout with abundant light, the kitchen features stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar. The spacious family room with high ceilings complements the formal living and dining room. Carpet and tile combination throughout. Step outside to a large fenced backyard with a patio, perfect for relaxation. Experience suburban bliss with modern tradition. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this remarkable single-story residence your very own!
